INFORMATION

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

CHANGES

* Version 2.0.0 (2022-06-25)
C: Rename 'interface' parameter to 'device'

* Version 1.11.0 (2022-04-24)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 7.1
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 7.0

* Version 1.10.0 (2021-10-15)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 7.0
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.9

* Version 1.9.0 (2021-05-02)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.9
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.8

* Version 1.8.1 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify Ansible file header (ansible_managed)

* Version 1.8.0 (2020-10-19)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.8
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.7

* Version 1.7.1 (2020-05-28)
B: Fix aggr lacpmode and lacptimeout options

* Version 1.7.0 (2020-05-26)
F: Add option to configure interface type aggr

* Version 1.6.0 (2020-05-19)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.7
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.6

* Version 1.5.0 (2020-02-22)
F: Add option to configure interface type trunk
F: Add options to configure trunkproto and trunkports

* Version 1.4.0 (2020-02-22)
F: Add option to configure default gateway (hostname_if_mygate)

* Version 1.3.0 (2019-10-18)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.6
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.5

* Version 1.2.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 1.1.0 (2019-04-27)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.5
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.4

* Version 1.0.2 (2019-02-13)
B: Correct dependency variable name (parameter has been renamed)

* Version 1.0.1 (2018-12-28)
E: Rename configuration file

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-28)
C: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'
C: Rename config parameters
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 0.5.1 (2018-11-30)
E: Define default value for 'item.state' parameter

* Version 0.5.0 (2018-10-20)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.4
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.3

* Version 0.4.0 (2018-05-22)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 0.3.2 (2018-05-17)
B: Correct template path

* Version 0.3.1 (2018-04-24)
E: Simplify role by removing 'template' option

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-04-04)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.3
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.2

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-02-20)
E: Simplify and improve Ansible role

* Version 0.1.0 (2017-09-04)
F: Initial release
